      "title": "Hingalgoda Tea Factory sets an all-time record price",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Hingalgoda Tea Factory situated in Hiniduma, Galle and managed by Tea Small Holder Factories, secured an attractive all- time record price of Rs. 3,300 per kg for a PF1 grade in the CTC Low Grown category at the tea auction held on 26 July.",
        "This line of tea was purchased by Sun Shine Tea Ltd and was marked and sold by John Keells."
      ],
